          Each recipe is a <b>composable primitive</b>. Mix them — a curator daemon that calls the proxy hop's gateway; a code-review tool that uses the MCP+SKILL combo for screenshot diffs; a spec builder that registers a custom memory backend for the implementation log. The shape stays the same: declare the primitive, hand the LLM a tight procedure, let the runtime route.
